name: Pathway to Freedom
description:
This is the final piece in the collection entitled 'Views from the Inside'. It tells the story of how I finally escaped Narcissistic Abuse and Serious Depression. This is my Path now, my road-map to escape towards a Brighter, Colourful, Tranquil and more Importantly, Creative New Future.

Discovering NFT's & Ai Art has truly changed my life for the better so Please join me on the journey as you will be extremely welcome

And if you are or have suffered Toxic Mental Abuse & Depression or Anxiety then I send you my warmest wishes and my thoughts: You deserve better and you Can change your life forever by taking the first steps out into the light towards Your Own Pathway to Freedom. It is never easy but the decisions that hold the greatest rewards are always the most difficult paths for us to tread.

Skarraquin x
